text: Pibanga jacareacanga is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 1995. It is known from Brazil and Ecuador.BioLib.cz - Pibanga jacareacanga. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1995
